---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms and Conditions — EMI Calculator"
  description="Read the terms and conditions for using EMI Calculator. By using this site, you agree to these terms."
>
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl mb-6" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">
      Terms and Conditions
    </h1>

    <div class="surface-card p-6 sm:p-8">
      <div class="space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted">
        <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> June 2026</p>

        <p>
          By accessing and using EMI Calculator ("this website"), you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and conditions outlined below. If you do not agree, please do not use this website.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text); font-family: var(--font-body);">Use of This Tool</h2>
        <p>
          EMI Calculator is provided free of charge for informational and educational purposes only. The calculations provided by this tool are estimates based on the inputs you provide. They should not be considered as financial advice or a binding offer from any lender.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text); font-family: var(--font-body);">Accuracy</h2>
        <p>
          While we strive to ensure the accuracy of our calculations, we make no warranties or representations regarding the accuracy, completeness, or reliability of the results. Actual loan terms, EMI amounts, and interest rates may vary based on your lender, credit profile, and other factors. Always verify calculations with your bank or financial institution before making borrowing decisions.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text); font-family: var(--font-body);">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          EMI Calculator and its creators shall not be held liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of this website or reliance on the information provided. You use this tool entirely at your own risk.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text); font-family: var(--font-body);">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          All content on this website, including text, design, code, and graphics, is the property of EMI Calculator unless otherwise stated. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without prior written permission.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text); font-family: var(--font-body);">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          This website may display advertisements through Google AdSense and use Google Analytics for usage tracking. These services are governed by their own terms and privacy policies. We are not responsible for the content of third-party advertisements.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text); font-family: var(--font-body);">Modifications</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting to this page. Your continued use of the website constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text); font-family: var(--font-body);">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about these terms, please <a href="/contact" class="text-primary underline">contact us</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
